{"id": 584, "genre": 1001, "title": "来，一句话证明你患有高贵的“松鼠症”！", "description": "“松鼠症”：表现为收藏购买大量自己喜欢的东西，就和要过冬的松鼠一样，然后都忘了自己藏哪儿了。", "record_count": 6014, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183613lEBMLWhfJ4Hg2cVv.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-21T11:14:21Z", "options": [{"id": 18946, "content": "收购了一堆有Feel的本子，十几年了…问题是最后也忘了在哪，估计…家里某个角落？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259007}, {"id": 18947, "content": "囤面膜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 261968}, {"id": 18949, "content": "鞋子买回来舍不得扔，或是懒得扔，衣服褪色了，一直在那里。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258672}, {"id": 18950, "content": "一堆女神的照片，比钱还多金。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259101}, {"id": 18952, "content": "买了很多平时根本不穿的衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 211343}, {"id": 19465, "content": "为了藏压岁钱经常放在一个貌似安全的地方 然后就不见了...?????", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216069}, {"id": 21769, "content": "我只是喜欢和松鼠一样囤积东西。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281379}, {"id": 18954, "content": "高中时翻出小学的买的笔记本然后很高兴地继续用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 214937}, {"id": 18955, "content": "各种转发mark后 过后根本忘记读", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241321}, {"id": 18956, "content": "收藏lamy", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 140168}, {"id": 18958, "content": "我才没有松鼠症呢?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262058}, {"id": 19471, "content": "收藏电影票火车票演出票景点门票", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 178075}, {"id": 19217, "content": "各种用过不舍得扔的东西，票根，盒子，卡片等等", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263459}, {"id": 18962, "content": "家里到处都是杂七杂八根本不在一个调上的杯子……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260829}, {"id": 18963, "content": "闺蜜清楚的说出来我买的旅行牙膏都放在哪里而我却不知道?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262096}, {"id": 19476, "content": "高达堆了一面墙，没时间做…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265030}, {"id": 18965, "content": "买的游戏 玩了几天就放起来灰了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164732}, {"id": 20757, "content": "笔买的多没用最后断油都用不了了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272575}, {"id": 18966, "content": "喜欢下载无数的app，到换手机的时候，有些应用还没有被我宠幸过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252204}, {"id": 24086, "content": "都上班了还习惯买一袋笔，然后……用一年都用不完。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 296562}, {"id": 18970, "content": "人不买一大堆囤着，那和咸鱼有什么区别。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 233507}, {"id": 18971, "content": "曾经收集了几大盒各种各样的电话充值卡，直到有了网上充值……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 261082}, {"id": 18972, "content": "下载了很多歌曲 然而下载后就再也没有听过了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262092}, {"id": 18973, "content": "有好几个抽屉的裤袜，看到喜欢的款就会买好几条，后来又有新欢了…就是越攒越多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234562}, {"id": 18975, "content": "咦，我今天刚拿的 Surface Book 放哪了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 188593}, {"id": 18980, "content": "喜欢就买 丢了再买  微笑 微笑 微笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236793}, {"id": 18981, "content": "岛国片算吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238150}, {"id": 18982, "content": "电器堆满屋子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 261580}, {"id": 19239, "content": "片子存了一个T的硬盘", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263548}, {"id": 20263, "content": "看到文具不买心里痒。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 269601}, {"id": 19240, "content": "各种包装盒包装袋 尤其是各种名牌的纸袋包装吊牌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263548}, {"id": 23852, "content": "每每出席大型活动，都收集很多美女手机号码，但没打过一次", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294023}, {"id": 18989, "content": "好几个硬盘，都是电影，总想什么时候一天一部看了，呵呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 173569}, {"id": 19246, "content": "喜欢收集一切旧的东西…尤其是看过的电影票！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263593}, {"id": 18991, "content": "觉得各种样式的衣服都需要一件", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147161}, {"id": 18996, "content": "茶", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254352}, {"id": 19252, "content": "每次都会拍下美好一刻的照片但是从来不会整理归类。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263683}, {"id": 20021, "content": "中学阶段一进文具店就疯狂的买笔芯，到现在都还没用完????", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 268090}, {"id": 18999, "content": "吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254352}, {"id": 19255, "content": "购物袋不舍得扔，老觉得以后有用，攒了一大堆", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263700}, {"id": 19256, "content": "收藏了很多图片，并没有去怎么看", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263716}, {"id": 19001, "content": "什么鬼？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262256}, {"id": 19002, "content": "原来这叫松鼠症啊，我有先见之明", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161620UvcFKN2XhSTy76z5.jpg", "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250865}, {"id": 19003, "content": "哈哈?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262256}, {"id": 18750, "content": "知乎收藏夹的文章", "image": null, "praise_count": 242, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 47721}, {"id": 18751, "content": "《盘点好听的却不容易找到的……歌曲》，然后就是九张图……", "image": null, "praise_count": 76, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232951}, {"id": 18752, "content": "印象笔记……", "image": null, "praise_count": 94, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 106986}, {"id": 18753, "content": "在哪兒了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 226630}, {"id": 18754, "content": "马！", "image": null, "praise_count": 160, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 134885}, {"id": 18755, "content": "打开网页收藏列表铺满整个屏幕", "image": null, "praise_count": 91, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258596}]}